    <content>The Assistant Director coordinates services and opportunities for Native American research and collaboration, serving as a resource for tribes, faculty, university staff, and students pursuing research about or with American Indian communities; develops course curriculum, training modules, and programming regarding Indigenous research methods and protocols, and provides outreach and support services for potential and current Native American graduate students. </content>
